                <strong>Overview</strong><br />"A permanent, refundable personal income
                tax credit for seniors and family members who live with them."
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="item-body-sbs">
            <p><strong>Basic Eligibility</strong><br />You need to be:</p>
            <ul>
