                    65 years old or older by the end of the year for which you are claiming
                    the credit
                </li>
            </ul>
            <p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; or</p>
            <ul>
                <li>living with a family member who is a senior</li>
                <li>Individuals at all income levels are eligible</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <a href="http://www.ontario.ca/taxes-and-benefits/healthy-homes-renovation-tax-credit" target="_blank"
