            <br />
            <a href="https://www.pxw1.snb.ca/snb7001/e/1000/CSS-FOL-40-9147E.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Vehicle
                Retrofitting And Accessible Vehicle Program - Application Form</a>
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="item-header">
        <h3 class="heading">The John Wood Foundation Inc. </h3>
    </div>
    <div class="item-body">
        <div class="item-body-sbs">
            <p><strong>Overview</strong><br>The John Wood Foundation Inc. focuses on raising money that will be
