                they need (up to $5000).</p>
        </div>
        <div class="item-body-sbs">
            <p><strong>Basic Eligibility</strong></p>
            <ul>
                <li>Must be a resident of New Brunswick.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <a href="http://www.thejohnwoodfoundation.org/apply-for-funding.html" target="_blank"
